{"tid":2177037,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"高級助理刑事檢控專員周天行: 林卓廷挑釁白衣人入閘打鬥 指揮黑衣人「唔好褪 頂住佢」","createTime":"2020-08-27T12:26:16.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-22T12:41:14.000Z","uid":240362,"like":5,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"c95a4241abd3aca2743a81c5c03427c61f7346d9","tid":2177037,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T12:26:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/news_%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/hk-discuss/2020/07/%E5%91%A8%E5%A4%A9%E8%A1%8C-%E6%B8%AF%E7%89%88%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%89%E6%B3%95-20200703163957_173f_large.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Fnews_%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2Fhk-discuss%2F2020%2F07%2F%25E5%2591%25A8%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E8%25A1%258C-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%2589%2588%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25AE%2589%25E6%25B3%2595-20200703163957_173f_large.jpg&h=10a348c3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n高級助理刑事檢控專員周天行目前屬刑事檢控科下的「特別職務」分科。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200827/Z76HEBEVW5GPXDWUGVAFU6WXL4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200827%2FZ76HEBEVW5GPXDWUGVAFU6WXL4%2F&d=Bx5vHrS2V4FMjGMjdccONs70t8psI8cu6Rjg0MoA49o%3D&h=ad2aa8cf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200827%2FZ76HEBEVW5GPXDWUGVAFU6WXL4%2F&h=97db195a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200827/Z76HEBEVW5GPXDWUGVAFU6WXL4/</a><br />\n<br />\n警方昨晨就去年7.21元朗事件，以暴動罪拘捕13人，包括遭白衣人施襲受傷、一直要求追查事件真相的民主黨立法會議員林卓廷，令原告變被告。其中七人今午提堂，據了解，控方指控整個暴動事件發生於當晚10時45分至11時02分，犯案過程只有17分鐘，對白衣人此前在街頭和港鐵站聚集及毆打事件隻字不提。控方指林當時指示黑衣人「大家千祈唔好褪，頂住佢（白衣人）」；又呼籲月台上市民「企落嚟幫手頂住佢」等行為，構成暴動。控方並指各被告口出狂言，語帶侮辱地挑釁白衣人。<br />\n<br />\n今午兩案主控官為高級助理刑事檢控專員周天行，案件由主任裁判官羅德泉處理。"},{"pid":"631245f4b0e50602b8e47c87a3c7a65552fc2d9c","tid":2177037,"uid":165749,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T12:28:10.000Z","msg":"痕痕<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad796661eb7e885b638102ba4110357fb98f3a17","tid":2177037,"uid":99391,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T12:28:19.000Z","msg":"其實除咗林卓廷之外<br />\n其他被告手足都好值得大家關注"},{"pid":"9d3bad73a1ddcf94eec62355ba2253006199742c","tid":2177037,"uid":51271,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T12:29:37.000Z","msg":"單憑一句，點砌呀！<br />\n<br />\n頂住白衫鄉黑唔好比佢攻擊"},{"pid":"e010b402530cfbcd37cd785798bac177c49e9d04","tid":2177037,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ad796661eb7e885b638102ba4110357fb98f3a17","tid":2177037,"uid":99391,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T12:28:19.000Z","msg":"其實除咗林卓廷之外<br />\n其他被告手足都好值得大家關注"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T12:30:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecaf8463b16d4adcb2bb646f9faba398861760dd","tid":2177037,"uid":21545,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T12:31:35.000Z","msg":"認住條pk  周天痕<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c386058ff65c43ca3fce1c5bd60e38ebfd8e316","tid":2177037,"uid":3212,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T12:32:41.000Z","msg":"特別職務係負責鳩up砌生豬肉？"},{"pid":"6e3e5800793fb4c3a7124460563873652cf031c2","tid":2177037,"uid":48083,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T12:35:13.000Z","msg":"斷章取義<br />\n<br />\n翻查林卓廷當日在社交網站Facebook的直播片段，他到達後已見地上有血迹，有不少在場人士向他表示較早前的襲擊情況，他也向在場人士表示已致電警方要求派員到場，其後白衣人出現並手持木棍等武器在閘外試圖襲擊閘內人士，閘內人士也有上前欲還擊，林卓廷不斷着閘內人士勿走前，當有白衣人打開了閘門後現場氣氛變得緊張，他一度着閘內人士勿退，否則白衣人反而會衝前，他在閘內向白衣人說：<strong><span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">「警察嚟緊拉你班仆街呀，拉你班仆街呀！你夠膽唔好走！企係度！」以及「你哋班仆街你夠膽唔好走！警察而家嚟緊，全部企晒喺度！」</span></span></strong>他其後在白衣人企圖攻入車廂施襲時，也曾於車廂內說「大男人頂住喺前面，女士企後面」。<br />\n<br />\n莊榮輝：林未抵埗前已聯絡警方到場監察<br />\n<br />\n當日與林卓廷一同前往元朗的民主黨莊榮輝接受《蘋果》查詢時指斥警方如以此檢控，是斷章取義，扭曲林卓廷說話的意思，他強調自己當日與林卓廷及另外一人，前往元朗途中，<strong><span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">在港鐵美孚站已聯絡元朗區傳媒聯絡組警員，通知有關元朗站情況，對方表明會派員到場。</span></span></strong>林當時亦有向對方表示會前往元朗站，以監察警方有否行動，而他們由美孚啟程到元朗，至少需時約20分鐘，他們認為警方派員也應差不多到場，故到場後向白衣人高呼勿走等，並非挑釁對方作出攻擊。莊反問警察捉賊高叫賊人勿走，又是否挑釁行為？至於車廂內，莊稱自己當時不在林卓廷身邊，但當時車廂內有女士及小朋友，「個個男性都諗住點樣保護幼弱，唔通叫女士細路仔頂住啊？」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200827/BA77VOQKQRDN3GXA5ZLHLDGYHE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200827%2FBA77VOQKQRDN3GXA5ZLHLDGYHE%2F&d=Bx5vHrS2V4FMjGMjdccONs70t8psI8cu6Rjg0MoA49o%3D&h=4d0ea69f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200827%2FBA77VOQKQRDN3GXA5ZLHLDGYHE%2F&h=1b6c5258\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200827/BA77VOQKQRDN3GXA5ZLHLDGYHE/</a>"},{"pid":"84d6c2e196b65552a6f72d02cf4782e6cb4afd63","tid":2177037,"uid":52876,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T12:37:22.000Z","msg":"頂住暴徒都係暴動？<br />\n班狗唔做野，市民一定比人任打？"},{"pid":"c81e6f484693cee2c6b10375d9d05722c6683fce","tid":2177037,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T12:39:48.000Z","msg":"東方加持<br />\n<br />\n唔晌屋企backup唔到<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/128807942654/posts/10158375669727655/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F128807942654%2Fposts%2F10158375669727655%2F&d=Bx5vHrS2V4FMjGMjdccONs70t8psI8cu6Rjg0MoA49o%3D&h=872bf3b1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/128807942654/posts/10158375669727655/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n0:10<br />\n林卓廷facebook截圖的確係吹雞入元朗站，不過係吹雞叫差佬入去啫<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/A6kcqkX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA6kcqkX.jpg&h=ff1cb13e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n0:20<br />\n你哋班x街，你夠膽唔好走，警察嚟緊(雖然突然好細聲，但仍然聽到)，全部企晒晌度<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果林卓廷係有參與暴動，咁黑警就係同林卓廷黨羽。"},{"pid":"2d1893ab063ebd89c2f2b28bc1875f9210bd360b","tid":2177037,"uid":26770,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T12:42:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2164999/page/2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2164999/page/2</a><br />\n<br />\n睇#48<br />\n呢條賤種周圍含就係doj 反人類小組其中一員<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">doj 成立左特別小組迫害異見人士<br />\n由一批想上位又無道德的人做<br />\n<br />\n副刑事檢控專員楊美琪<br />\n<strong>高級助理刑事檢控專員周天行</strong><br />\n助理刑事檢控專員陳淑儀<br />\n仲有一個係我講的助理刑事檢控專員蕭啟業<br />\n<br />\n而西環為合理化doj玩政治迫害<br />\n<br />\n當時搵左香港理工大學專業及持續教育學院講師陳偉強呢條共狗合理化成單野<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"94ae42fbfcf3e2859a5bb1d03fcece06da55e1a4","tid":2177037,"uid":34065,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T12:42:39.000Z","msg":"屌你老母 被班垃圾白衣暴徒追打緊 警黑勾結 又無黑警黎執法<br />\n咁有人見義勇為 保護無辜市民唔好比人打 頂住班白衣暴徒生番<br />\n有乜問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔通等班白衣暴徒生番 打死哂啲無辜市民?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba45875facd47baa7a1464d57db574c6dbc9d648","tid":2177037,"uid":323319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c95a4241abd3aca2743a81c5c03427c61f7346d9","tid":2177037,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T12:26:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/news_%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/hk-discuss/2020/07/%E5%91%A8%E5%A4%A9%E8%A1%8C-%E6%B8%AF%E7%89%88%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%89%E6%B3%95-20200703163957_173f_large.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Fnews_%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2Fhk-discuss%2F2020%2F07%2F%25E5%2591%25A8%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E8%25A1%258C-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%2589%2588%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25AE%2589%25E6%25B3%2595-20200703163957_173f_large.jpg&h=10a348c3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />